otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Hi%E1%BA%BFu-T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/T%C3%A2y-giang-nguy%E1%BB%87t-%C4%90an-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BB%93/poem-4BHCyKKJqh04Q-pytmEdIw">Tây giang nguyệt - Đan Dương Hồ - 西江月－丹陽湖</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Hi%E1%BA%BFu-T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/author-77k7d_i26Q3zI_gu_1iz-w">Trương Hiếu Tường</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%87nh-H%E1%BB%93-S%E1%BB%9F/Thi%E1%BA%BFu-ni%C3%AAn-h%C3%A0nh-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-q3_NPmzPKb8u4VYzxyoQxA">Thiếu niên hành kỳ 1 - 少年行其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%87nh-H%E1%BB%93-S%E1%BB%9F/author-mH2tWe7RQ4SVhKlHTfKyoQ">Lệnh Hồ Sở</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng-C%C3%A1t/Ti%E1%BB%81u-%C3%B4ng/poem-s7UL43hnVID8c76IoZH0dA">Tiều ông - 樵翁</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng-C%C3%A1t/author-vxzuMqDTeI2lyy4Fg1mXXg">Tưởng Cát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-Qu%C3%A1n-vu-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-d%E1%BA%A1-qu%C3%A1-xu%C3%A2n-th%C3%AC/poem-Dw900MWP39rk84Ri54uFpw">Vô đề (Quán vu trường dạ quá xuân thì) - 無題（慣于長夜過春時）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/author-TXAaCmjdRWIV6MkCYE1psQ">Lỗ Tấn</a>)<br></div>	</div>
